  "description": "Yoke and harness systems for oxen, horses, and mules. Applications: plowing (ox-drawn plow breaks sod that hand tools cannot), cart and wagon pulling (500-1500 kg per animal), water lifting (animal-powered sakia), grain milling (horse or ox-powered millstones), mining hoisting (horse whim: 3-4 HP). Primary motive power source until steam engines.",
